query:
SELECT 
  pwi.id as wave_item_id,
  pwi.productName,
  po.customerOrderNumber,
  CASE WHEN po.customerOrderNumber IS NULL THEN 'NULL' ELSE 'OK' END as status
FROM pickingWaveItems pwi
LEFT JOIN inventory inv ON (
  pwi.locationId = inv.locationId 
  AND pwi.productId = inv.productId 
  AND pwi.batch = inv.batch
)
LEFT JOIN pickingReservations pr ON inv.id = pr.inventoryId
LEFT JOIN pickingOrders po ON pr.pickingOrderId = po.id
WHERE pwi.waveId = 30002
ORDER BY pwi.id;
